{"tid":475803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[希臘政府要救人呀］19歲大波長腿希臘美少女運毒來港機場斷正","createTime":"2017-11-21T12:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T07:19:53.000Z","uid":39539,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8992e1fec4082be3eb594930641d37f9dfbbc9df","tid":475803,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:41:54.000Z","msg":"海關機場科人員於昨午(20日)，在香港國際機場截查一名由埃塞俄比亞來港的歐洲裔女子，在其隨身背囊暗格夾層內發現2.6公斤懷疑可卡因，約值240萬元，案件交由毒品調查科跟進。海關表示，被捕女子19歲，報稱任職模特兒，初時由西歐乘飛機前往埃塞俄比亞，逗留數天後才轉往香港，現時她已被落案控以一項販運危險藥物的罪名，明天於西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/204149_6113b4894bcaf2d9f06e8aeaa607c486.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F204149_6113b4894bcaf2d9f06e8aeaa607c486.jpg&h=950f0961&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33fb81eb177b2217eaa304de9c2199dc23e33174","tid":475803,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:49:37.000Z","msg":"淫腳"},{"pid":"2d83b2fe76a7a91864bb0d67d1223d484a46c022","tid":475803,"uid":3109,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"我想要左右兩件海關妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49218cf8869ab22293a748b1113b4cf2e4515947","tid":475803,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:25:57.000Z","msg":"咁撚高係咪變性人 .."},{"pid":"1b2ce9d0f6236593ec3f23026032740984bb31e5","tid":475803,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:30:19.000Z","msg":"基因優越，高撚過東亞人幾撚多"},{"pid":"7ce549a8b71b77bbf9947befbc1c97c2be1192fd","tid":475803,"uid":39200,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:45:51.000Z","msg":"點解海關都要蒙面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36eb0c0042a5c80639a4d3189b9f3472f73d01ff","tid":475803,"uid":41508,"like